@startuml UC_15_Individual
left to right direction
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam actorStyle awesome
skinparam usecase {
  BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
  BorderColor #1565C0
  FontSize 11
}

title UC-15: View Score Explanation

actor "User\n(A01/A02/A03)" as USER
actor "System Backend\n(A04)" as A04
actor "AI Assistant" as AI

rectangle "SmartLocateSG" {
  usecase "UC-15 View Score Explanation" as UC15
  usecase "UC-13 Drop POI Pin and Get Site Score" as R13
}

USER --> UC15
A04 --> UC15
AI --> UC15

UC15 ..> R13 : <<extend>>

note right of UC15
Pre: Refer corresponding sequence precondition.
Flow: Main interaction follows sequence messages.
AC/EX: Alternate and exception branches traced from sequence.
end note

@enduml
